<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-10-1304 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper describes the self-contained coal handling plant of Block 5in the Altbach-Deizisau Power Plant complex. Particular emphasis is givento the equipment at the plant, which includes a car unloading stationan 'emergency' discharge/'emergency' feeding point, a boom stacker anda conveyor system. The construction of the plant had to fulfil variouscriteria including low energy and personnel costs, high availability,a high degree of flexibility, job safety, minimal environmental impactand architectonics harmony. The plant has been in operation since 1985and has so far fulfilled these criteria. 3 refs., 11 figs., 2 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>